query:
SELECT id as "id!: i32", 
severity as "severity!: AuditLogSeverity", 
created_at as "created_at!: UtcDateTime", 
kind as "kind!: String", 
subkind as "subkind!: String", 
context as "context!: String", 
loggable_type as "loggable_type!: Option < String >", 
loggable_id as "loggable_id!: Option < String >" FROM audit_log_entries WHERE (NOT $1::boolean OR id = $2::int4) AND (NOT $3::boolean OR id = ANY(CAST($4 as int4[])) ) AND (NOT $5::boolean OR severity = $6::audit_log_severity) AND (NOT $7::boolean OR created_at = $8::timestamptz) AND (NOT $9::boolean OR kind = $10::varchar) AND (NOT $11::boolean OR subkind = $12::varchar) AND (NOT $13::boolean OR context = $14::text) AND (NOT $15::boolean OR loggable_type = $16::varchar) AND (NOT $17::boolean OR loggable_id = $18::varchar) ORDER BY 
      (CASE ($19 = 'Id' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Id' AND $20) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'Severity' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN severity ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Severity' AND $20) WHEN true THEN severity ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'CreatedAt' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'CreatedAt' AND $20) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'Kind' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN kind ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Kind' AND $20) WHEN true THEN kind ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'Subkind' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN subkind ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Subkind' AND $20) WHEN true THEN subkind ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'Context' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN context ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Context' AND $20) WHEN true THEN context ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'LoggableType' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN loggable_type ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'LoggableType' AND $20) WHEN true THEN loggable_type ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'LoggableId' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN loggable_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'LoggableId' AND $20) WHEN true THEN loggable_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
     LIMIT $21 OFFSET $22
